| **Multi-agent orchestration** | **MOCK** | Agents exist but workers execute tasks. No inter-agent communication. DAG in orchestrator supports it but pipeline doesn't use it. |
| **Autonomous debugging** | **MOCK** | BugHunter imported but never invoked. No crash analysis. |
| **Cloud deployment** | **UNTESTED** | FTP logic exists but requires credentials; hardcoded to InfinityFree defaults. No actual deploy tested. |

